OL,3,CWoman murdered 'shell of a man'
OL,4,Chusband after birthday night out
OL,6,FA woman has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fstabbing her husband to death in their
OL,8,Fhome after downing cocktails on her
OL,9,Fbirthday night out.
OL,11,FDuring a two-week trial, heard how
OL,12,FLisa Ellwood, 40, attacked Ryan
OL,13,FEllwood at their home in Greenwood
OL,14,FCourt, , on 29 August last year.
OL,16,FShe stabbed him with a knife, piercing
OL,17,Fhis rib, lung and aorta.
