OL,6,FEllwood claimed to have no
OL,7,Frecollection of the attack, and even
OL,8,Fsuggested her 16-year-old daughter
OL,9,Fcould have been responsible.
OL,11,FThe court heard the couple had visited
OL,12,Fa bar in the town earlier in the
OL,13,Fevening and that Ellwood had "around
OL,14,Fsix" cocktails.
OL,16,FA supervisor at the Blind Pig pub said
OL,17,Fhe had seen them that night and they
OL,18,Fwere in "good spirits."
OL,20,FHe said: "They seemed to be having a
OL,21,Flaugh and a joke all evening."
