OL,6,FBut during the trial friends of Ryan
OL,7,Ftold how he had "deteriorated into the
OL,8,Fshell of a man" over the course of the
OL,9,Fmarriage.
OL,11,FIn his closing speech to the jury on
OL,12,FMonday, prosecutor Craig Hassall KC
OL,13,Fsaid: "Those people who knew him
OL,14,Fbefore or through the relationship
OL,15,Fdescribed him in their witness
OL,16,Fstatements as a quiet and kind-hearted
OL,17,Fman who would do anything for anyone.
