OL,6,F"They also said throughout the
OL,7,Frelationship he became more
OL,8,Fintroverted and deteriorated into a
OL,9,Fshell of a man."
OL,11,FThe jury heard that Ellwood sought to
OL,12,Fportray herself as a "battered wife"
OL,13,Fand told doctors she had been the
OL,14,Fvictim of domestic violence.
OL,16,FHowever, witnesses recalled her
OL,17,Fattacking her husband in public, even
OL,18,Ffighting with a staff member at a pub
OL,19,Fafter Mr Ellwood took a selfie with
OL,20,Ftwo work colleagues.
