OL,6,FAfter being found guilty on Tuesday,
OL,7,F12 March, Ellwood is due to be
OL,8,Fsentenced on Wednesday afternoon.
OL,10,FAs she was led from the dock into
OL,11,Fcustody, cries could be heard
OL,12,Fthroughout the courtroom.
